				 *** Text Processing using Spacy *** 


================================ Paragraph 1 =================================

Big Data Analytics: A Literature Review  

------------------- Sentence 1 -------------------

Big Data Analytics: A Literature Review   


>> Tokens are: 
[Big, Data, Analytics, :, Literature, Review,  ] 

>> PoS Tags are: 
[('Big', 'PROPN'), ('Data', 'PROPN'), ('Analytics', 'PROPN'), (':', 'PUNCT'), ('Literature', 'PROPN'), ('Review', 'PROPN'), (' ', 'SPACE')] 

>> Dependency Tags are: 
[('Big', 'amod'), ('Data', 'compound'), ('Analytics', 'ROOT'), (':', 'punct'), ('Literature', 'compound'), ('Review', 'appos'), (' ', 'nummod')]

>> Bigrams: 
[[Big, Data], [Data, Analytics], [Analytics, :], [:, Literature], [Literature, Review], [Review,  ]]

>> Trigrams: 
[[Big, Data, Analytics], [Data, Analytics, :], [Analytics, :, Literature], [:, Literature, Review], [Literature, Review,  ]]

>> Noun Phrases are: 
[Big Data Analytics, A Literature Review]

>> Named Entities are: 
[('Big Data Analytics: A Literature Review', 'ORG')]
